or: \"var(--secondary)\", color: \"var(--secondary-foreground)\", fontSize: \"var(--font-size-label)\", minHeight: \"48px\" }}>\n                    取消\n                  </button>\n                  <button onClick={handleImportText}\n                    className=\"flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg\"\n                    style={{ backgroundColor: \"var(--primary)\", color: \"var(--primary-foreground)\", fontSize: \"var(--font-size-label)\", minHeight: \"48px\" }}>\n                    导入\n                  </button>\n                </div>\n              </motion.div>\n            </motion.div>\n          )}\n        </AnimatePresence>\n\n        {/* Delete Confirm */}\n        <AnimatePresence>\n          {showDeleteConfirm && (\n            <motion.div\n              initial={{ opacity: 0 }} animate={{ opacity: 1 }} exit={{ opacity: 0 }}\n              className=\"fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center\"\n              style={{ backgroundColor: \"rgba(0,0,0,0.4)\" }}\n            >\n              <motion.div\n                initial={{ scale: 0.95 }} animate={{ scale: 1 }} exit={{ scale: 0.95 }}\n                className=\"w-[85vw] max-w-sm rounded-xl p-4\"\n                style={{ backgroundColor: \"var(--background)\" }}\n              >\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\">\n                  <AlertTriangle size={24} style={{ color: \"var(--destructive)\" }} />\n                  <h3 style={{ fontSize: \"var(--font-size-body)\", fontWeight: \"var(--font-weight-semibold)\", color: \"var(--foreground)\" }}>\n                    确认删除\n                  </h3>\n                </div>\n                <p style={{ fontSize: \"var(--font-size-label)\", color: \"var(--muted-foreground)\", marginBottom: \"var(--spacing-sm)\" }}>\n                  以下病人不在导入列表中：\n                </p>\n                <div className=\"max-h-40 overflow-y-auto mb-3\">\n                  {toDelete.map((p) => (\n                    <div key={p.id} style={{ fontSize: \"var(--font-size-label)\", color: \"var(--foreground)\", padding: \"4px 0\" }}>\n                      {p.bedNumber} {p.name}\n                    </div>\n                  ))}\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n                  <button onClick={() => setShowDeleteConfirm(false)}\n                    className=\"flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg\"\n                    style={{ backgroundColor: \"var(--secondary)\", color: \"var(--secondary-foreground)\", fontSize: \"var(--font-size-label)\", minHeight: \"48px\" }}>\n                    取消\n                  </button>\n                  <button onClick={handleConfirmDelete}\n                    className=\"flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg\"\n                    style={{ backgroundColor: \"var(--destructive)\", color: \"white\", fontSize: \"var(--font-size-label)\", minHeight: \"48px\" }}>\n                    确认删除\n                  </button>\n                </div>\n              </motion.div>\n            </motion.div>\n          )}\n        </AnimatePresence>\n      </main>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n","file_path":"/workspace/frontend/src/pages/DataManagement.tsx"},"tool_response":"Successfully overwrote file: /workspace/frontend/src/pages/DataManagement.tsx","call_id":"call_00_1KBYpWfQbWsJ6iSRzpob7487","tool_use_id":"call_00_1KBYpWfQbWsJ6iSRzpob7487","agent_type":"cli","permission_mode":"dontAsk","client":"CLI","version":"2.99.0","generation_id":"54dafd4f9a424cf88af537062127e6d1","model":"deepseek-v4-pro"}
